updates.update_content:
Ok Joe and I are off to the Expo tomorrow, we will try to check in, but might be a tad exhausted with all the Wasteland Justice demoing that will be going on, to say much here.  
In the meantime we would like to leave you with some exciting news;
Our board will have a second side to offer a different and more dangerous track for those up for the challenge!  This new board has the clever working title of "Side B."
